{"tid":2140021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：空氣傳播、食魚或水產而感染病毒的機會很低","createTime":"2020-08-04T16:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T16:59:12.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a7c74526e3ac32f11695d06512e7833c3e1312","tid":2140021,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"袁國勇：空氣傳播、食魚或水產而感染病毒的機會很低<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n&quot;【Now新聞台】港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇到街市視察及收集環境樣本，他稱現時未肯定病毒散播途徑，但認為空氣傳播、食魚或水產而感染的機會很低，相信由人或動物帶病毒透過接觸感染機會較大。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400508&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZearHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=2db7894e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400508&h=0a9982de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400508</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">大家可以放心繼續食海產</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce6d3b73658e1ffad4b5b522600018e4b410e44","tid":2140021,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"大家可以放心繼續食海產<br />\n<br />\n波特王: 不去關心黃安反而去關心沒有肺的三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a19a8909d55b719f9110e43d68b44a8b46f9cb","tid":2140021,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"黨話三文魚播毒<br />\n相信三文魚不屬海產"}]}